[21/12/2019 22:27:26] <font color="#ffffff">Muerto.</font>
[21/12/2019 22:27:26] <font color="#00ffff">¿En serio, Daesh?</font>
[21/12/2019 22:27:28] <font color="#00ffff">Te salvó la vida.</font>
